author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: I just love that "LALAURIEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEEE, SHOW YOURSELF" line. What an actress!
"I'm sorry for your loss" and proceeds to eat chicken leg.
"If I wanted you dead, you would be..."  Most SAVAGE line EVER!!! LOL

I love how when Marie says "..to never reunite with loved ones in the realm beyond but instead to be alone, sealed up in your unmarked grave..." just reveals how she feels about her situation with being immortal.  And the unmarked grave part is a foreshadow to how Marie's body parts were scattered by Delphine in the future and therefore being unmarked.
